You are working on the GitHub repo: https://github.com/abhichhn93/4g-5g-ims-simulators

This repo has three C++17 simulators:
- 4g-simulator/ — 4G EPC (eNB, MME, HSS, SGW, PGW, PCRF) using real S1AP ASN.1 PER, GTPv2, Diameter
- ims-simulator/ — IMS/VoLTE (P-CSCF, S-CSCF, MTAS, IMS-HSS) using SIP/SDP, Diameter Cx/Rx
- 5g-simulator/ — 5G Core SBA (gNB, AMF, UDM, NRF) using HTTP+JSON SBI

The owner is a Senior C++ Telecom Engineer (ex-Samsung MME/AMF, ex-LG VoLTE). 
This is both a portfolio project and an educational resource for engineers 
studying 3GPP protocols. All changes must preserve the 3-level logging system 
(BEGINNER / ENGINEER / INTERVIEW mode) throughout.

