5. REAL SDP IN SIP INVITE
   Alongside real SIP text, add proper SDP body to INVITE and 200 OK:
   Content-Type: application/sdp
   Body:
     v=0
     o=ue1 0 0 IN IP4 127.0.0.1
     s=VoLTE Call
     c=IN IP4 127.0.0.1
     t=0 0
     m=audio 49170 RTP/AVP 116
     a=rtpmap:116 AMR-WB/16000
     a=fmtp:116 mode-set=0,1,2;max-red=0
   This is IR.92 compliant. Wireshark will decode it as real VoLTE SDP.

