6. X2/S1 HANDOVER in 4G simulator
   Add command: HO <ue_id>
   Simulate intra-frequency S1 handover flow:
   Step 1: MME receives Handover Required from source eNB
   Step 2: MME sends Handover Request to target eNB  
   Step 3: Target eNB sends Handover Request Ack
   Step 4: MME sends Handover Command to source eNB
   Step 5: eNB sends eNB Status Transfer
   Step 6: MME sends Path Switch Request to SGW (Modify Bearer)
   Step 7: SGW acknowledges, MME sends UE Context Release
   All steps written to pcap. Full BEGINNER/ENGINEER/INTERVIEW narration.
   Reference: TS 36.413 §8.4

